{
  "texts": [
    "This specific graph contained 501,000 unique binding affinities encompassing around 360,000 unique molecules and 2989 unique target-IDs.",
    "The outcome of this mapping effort revealed a total of 8351 distinct protein structures associated with 744 unique target-IDs.",
    "By refining the drug-target graph to exclusively include target-IDs with annotated PDB structures, the modified graph encompassed around 263,000 unique binding affinities spanning around 208,000 unique molecules and 744 unique target-IDs.",
    "The connection between PDB-IDs and target-IDs within ChEMBL was facilitated through UNIPROT-IDs, given that both databases provide UNIPROT-IDs for individual proteins.",
    "Numerous drug targets exhibit multiple binding sites, including orthosteric sites and various allosteric sites 94."
  ]
}